text: Lariboisière Hospital (French: Hôpital Lariboisière) is a hospital in Paris. It is one of Europe's largest hospitals. It was created in 1854. It is a partner of the Université Paris Cité.HOPITAL LARIBOISIERE == References == == Further reading == * Hôpital Lariboisière Category:1850s establishments in France Category:1854 establishments in Europe Category:Hospitals in Paris Category:University hospitals in France
